Titolo: Age of Chivalry

Anno: 2007

Descrizione: Age of Chivalry is a multiplayer-focused total conversion modification for Valve's Half-Life 2 using the Source engine. Founded by Rickard Drakborn, Jeff Simmons and Scott Chipman, and developed by a group of independent developers called Team Chivalry, the mod features a medieval theme and aims to provide enjoyable close-combat battles.

Genere: Non specificato


Valutazione: N/A
